Pre-Game Insights: The Pakistan Cricket Team is set to face Ireland at home in a three-match T20I series, following a drawn series with New Zealand.
Pakistan T20I squad: Babar Azam (captain), Abrar Ahmed, Azam Khan, Fakhar Zaman, Haris Rauf, Hasan Ali, Iftikhar Ahmed, Imad Wasim, Abbas Afridi, Mohammad Amir, Mohammad Rizwan, Irfan Khan, Naseem Shah, Saim Ayub, Salman Agha, Shadab Khan, Shaheen Afridi, Usman Khan.
Ireland T20I squad: Paul Stirling (captain), Mark Adair, Ross Adair, Andrew Balbirnie, Curtis Campher, Gareth Delany, George Dockrell, Graham Hume, Barry McCarthy, Neil Rock, Harry Tector, Lorcan Tucker, Ben White, Craig Young.
Where can you watch PAK vs IRE T20 live: Indian fans can watch Pakistan vs Ireland T20 series live streaming on Fancode app.
When will PAK vs IRE T20 series start?: Pakistan will lock horns with Ireland in the opening match which will begin on May10.
What is the venue of PAK vs IRE T20 seri: All the three matches of the Pakistan vs Ireland T20 series will be played in Dublin at the Clontarf Cricket Club.
Pakistan vs Ireland T20I series schedule: 1st T20I: Friday, 10 May 2024 – Dublin – 7 PM Local Time (PKT) / 7:30 PM IST, 2nd T20I: Sunday, 12 May 2024 – Dublin – 7 PM Local Time (PKT) / 7:30 PM IST, 3rd T20I: Tuesday, 14 May 2024 – Dublin – 7 PM Local Time (PKT) / 7:30 PM IST
